rows.label: qst701304_msg0002
rows.name:
But why...?
If he's dead, then I guess it's all over.

rows.label: qst701304_msg0003
rows.name:
At the very least, he did accomplish
his goal...

rows.label: qst701304_msg0004
rows.name: We should let Sarah know about this.

rows.label: qst701304_msg0005
rows.name:
His life was the price he paid to
get the proof he needed...

rows.label: qst701304_msg0007
rows.name:
But first, we should bury the body. A
traveling performer like him deserves
a better resting place than this.
